                                <img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.cts.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F202405%2F202405072320232_l.jpg" border="0" alt="王品「初瓦、嚮辣」西門店未驗出諾羅 北市府同意5/13復業 | 華視新聞" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
